<main>
  <div class="container text-center">
    <div class="overlay-header mb-4">
      <% if @user&.level&.name&.include?("1") %>
        <h3 class= mb-4>Every decision shapes your path to mastery!</h3>
        <%= image_tag "icon_level1.png", alt: "Level 1", class: "img-fluid mb-3", style: "max-width: 150px;" %>
        <p class= lead>Start your financial journey by learning how to save smart. Make choices that grow your money, avoid common pitfalls, and watch your nest egg take shape.</p>
      <% elsif @user&.level&.name&.include?("2") %>
        <h3 class= mb-4>Take your skills to the next level!</h3>
        <%= image_tag "icon_level2.png", alt: "Level 2", class: "img-fluid mb-3", style: "max-width: 150px;" %>
        <p class= lead>Learn how to make money work for you. Explore investments, interest, and smart strategies that earn while you focus on other adventures.</p>
        <p class= lead>Can you unlock the secret to steady, hands-off income?</p>
      <% elsif @user&.level&.name&.include?("3") %>
        <h3 class= mb-4>Diversify your income!</h3>
        <%= image_tag "icon_level3.png", alt: "Level 3", class: "img-fluid mb-3", style: "max-width: 150px;" %>
        <p class= lead>Become a true Wealth Wizard: manage multiple streams, balance risks and rewards, and discover how to maximize your earnings.</p>
        <p class= lead>The more you explore, the more your financial empire grows!</p>
      <% else %>
        <%= image_tag "logo.png", alt: "Wealth Wizard", class: "img-fluid mb-3", style: "max-width: 150px;" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
